import React from 'react'; import { useAuth } from '../../contexts/AuthContext'; import { DollarSign, Play, Users, TrendingUp } from 'lucide-react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import AnimatedButton from '../../components/UI/AnimatedButton'; import GlassCard from '../../components/UI/GlassCard'; const DashboardPage = () => { const { user } = useAuth(); const stats = [ { name: 'Current Balance', value: `$${user?.balance?.toFixed(2) || '0.00'}`, icon: DollarSign, color: 'text-green-600', bgColor: 'bg-green-100' }, { name: 'Ads Watched', value: user?.adsWatched || 0, icon: Play, color: 'text-blue-600', bgColor: 'bg-blue-100' }, { name: 'Total Earned', value: `$${user?.totalEarned?.toFixed(2) || '0.00'}`, icon: TrendingUp, color: 'text-purple-600', bgColor: 'bg-purple-100' }, { name: 'Referrals', value: user?.referralCount || 0, icon: Users, color: 'text-orange-600', bgColor: 'bg-orange-100' } ]; return (
{/* Welcome Section */}

Welcome back, {user?.firstName || user?.username}!

Ready to watch some ads and earn money?

{/* Stats Grid */}
{stats.map((stat) => (

{stat.name}

{stat.value}

 ))}
{/* Quick Actions */}

Quick Actions

Watch Ads Withdraw Earnings Invite Friends
); }; export default DashboardPage;
